      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOOSEBUMPS RICO (8) finished fourth last time at this track but could not have been more impressive before that in his handy 24.00 win at this track over 425m. Has the ability and looks hard to top. DAVE (1) has been below best and missed the frame last couple, finishing 6th (16.77) last time in a Grade 5 at Healesville. Has never been out of the money this course and distance including one win. Likely to be about the money. INSINUATING (2) scored an on-pace win two back then gave a start and could manage only 5th at Horsham (23.64) last time. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from four starts. Cannot be underestimated. GRAFFITI (3) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
